    Interface Description
    HandyRuleBuilder
    From the entry methods at UrlMappingRuleSet, there are two possible flow of rule configuration: UrlMappingRuleSet.add(String, String): Once the target path is configured by entry method, the only operations can be performed is to set rule attributes related values, such as id, rule attribute, extra path variables, rule matcher, priority, etc.
